==落地签==
{{flag|Kenya}}和{{flag|Uganda}}公民可在抵达时获得落地签。

2018年11月签署了一项协议，允许在抵达时给予[[阿联酋|阿联酋]]公民落地签，有效期最长为30天，尚未实施<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.khaleejtimes.com/travel/20181129/now-visa-free-travel-to-this-exotic-tourist-destination |title=存档副本 |access-date=2019-04-29 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605041337/https://www.khaleejtimes.com/travel/20181129/now-visa-free-travel-to-this-exotic-tourist-destination |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2019年3月宣布将扩展落地签政策，塞拉利昂也将投资开发电子签证系统<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.travelpulse.com/news/destinations/sierra-leone-announces-new-e-visa-and-visa-on-arrival-program.html |title=Sierra Leone Announces New E-Visa and Visa on Arrival Program |access-date=2019-04-29 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919124439/https://www.travelpulse.com/news/destinations/sierra-leone-announces-new-e-visa-and-visa-on-arrival-program.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

